    "media:imagetext": "Not Transferable\nNot a credit card\n•PAN AM.\nSign in ink here\n2014.163\n1003\nis a Pan Am Frequent Traveler and a participant in Pan Am WorldPass.\nPresentation of this card throughout the world is your assurance of the most\npersonal assistance and consideration.\nTo receive mileage credit, use your WorldPass number when you make your\nreservations and at check-in. Please carry this card with you whenever you\ntravel to ensure that your WorldPass number is readily available.\nWorldPass Service Center 1-800-348-8000\nPan Am Reservations 1-800-221-1111\nThis card remains the property of Pan American World Airways, Inc.\nand must be surrendered upon request by a Pan Am Representative.",
